{
  "texts": [
    "The annotation, carried out by medical and terminology professionals, has produced quality data, as shown by the high inter-annotator agreement achieved.",
    "Even though this resource lacks a rich variety of entity types, we have shown that competitive results can be obtained at its current state.",
    "Our tests come along resources and code to replicate and generalize our preliminary outcomes.Given that this corpus includes texts also available in English, if needed, parallel texts may be collected in the future.",
    "Similar documents or the same translated texts are available in PubMed, EudraCT or SciELO [82].",
    "Therefore, similar corpora can be collected and annotated in other languages."
  ]
}